profile:
We are proud to be one of the best professional locksmith service providers in Barrie, Wasaga Beach, Collingwood, Blue Mountain and the surrounding area of South Georgian Bay. To be one of the best means being able to provide prompt, dependable, quality workmanship and personable service at reasonable rates with high standards. 
Services include
• Key Cutting– Re Key Service 
• New Door Hardware and locks 
• Gate Locks – Padlocks - Cabinet Locks
• Safes 	
• Lock repair or installation
• Emergency Opening when locked out 
• Door Closers – Exit Devices - Door Repair
• Electronic Key Pad Replacement
• Master Key or Maison Key
• High Security Locks & High Security Keys
• 24 7 Mobile Emergency Locksmith Service - Because we care all the time.
Action Lock is a member of TAOL- The Association Of Ontario Locksmiths and certified by ALOA - Associated Locksmiths of America. Your Safety is our number one priority and Customer Satisfaction is KEY.
